query:
SET @riv_id = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name LIKE '%Riverside%' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1);

-- Cardiac protocols (4500 series)
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, protocolEffectiveDate, protocolYear, createdAt)
VALUES 
(@riv_id, '4501', 'Chest Pain/ACS', 'Cardiac', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Chest Pain and Acute Coronary Syndrome. 12-lead ECG, aspirin, nitroglycerin, and STEMI activation.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4502', 'Bradycardia', 'Cardiac', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Bradycardia. Atropine, transcutaneous pacing, and dopamine infusion.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4503', 'Tachycardia', 'Cardiac', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Tachycardia. Vagal maneuvers, adenosine, and synchronized cardioversion.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4504', 'Cardiogenic Shock', 'Cardiac', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Cardiogenic Shock. Fluid management and vasopressor support.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4505', 'Post Resuscitation Care', 'Cardiac', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Post Resuscitation Care after ROSC. Hemodynamic support and neuroprotection.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),

-- Medical protocols (4600 series)
(@riv_id, '4601', 'Altered Mental Status', 'Medical', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Altered Mental Status. Assessment, blood glucose, and naloxone consideration.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4602', 'Behavioral Emergencies', 'Medical', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Behavioral Emergencies. Scene safety, de-escalation, and chemical restraint.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4603', 'Seizures', 'Medical', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Seizures. Airway protection and benzodiazepine administration.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4604', 'Stroke/CVA', 'Medical', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Stroke/CVA. Stroke scale assessment, blood glucose, and stroke center transport.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4605', 'Diabetic Emergencies', 'Medical', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Diabetic Emergencies. Hypoglycemia treatment with dextrose and glucagon.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4606', 'Allergic Reaction/Anaphylaxis', 'Medical', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Allergic Reaction and Anaphylaxis. Epinephrine, diphenhydramine, and steroids.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4607', 'Overdose/Poisoning', 'Medical', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Overdose and Poisoning. Naloxone, supportive care, and specific antidotes.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4608', 'Pain Management', 'Medical', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Pain Management. Fentanyl and morphine administration.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4609', 'Nausea/Vomiting', 'Medical', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Nausea and Vomiting. Ondansetron administration.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),

-- Environmental protocols (4700 series)
(@riv_id, '4701', 'Hyperthermia', 'Environmental', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Hyperthermia. Cooling measures and fluid resuscitation.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4702', 'Hypothermia', 'Environmental', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Hypothermia. Passive and active rewarming.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4703', 'Drowning/Submersion', 'Environmental', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Drowning and Submersion. Airway management and warming.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4704', 'Bites and Stings', 'Environmental', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Bites and Stings. Wound care and anaphylaxis management.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW());
